{"tid":2510782,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"第一滴血｜沙田瓏珀山2,400萬元四房撻定 殺定120萬元","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T05:30:33.000Z","uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"687ce9e973b4ef247e2bf0c81cd7be2885c3cae6","tid":2510782,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"第一滴血｜沙田瓏珀山2,400萬元四房撻定 殺定120萬元<br />\n51分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n沙田瓏珀山錄首宗撻定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210430/UNMI23JYSFAV5KHS2CMMMMG3GM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210430%2FUNMI23JYSFAV5KHS2CMMMMG3GM%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e3339899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210430%2FUNMI23JYSFAV5KHS2CMMMMG3GM%2F&h=445e9039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210430/UNMI23JYSFAV5KHS2CMMMMG3GM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由新地（016）發展的沙田多石街新盤瓏珀山，近日推出招標頻錄成交，今日再沽7伙。不過，項目卻最新錄得首宗撻定，一伙2,400萬元售出的四房戶近日交易沒進展，料遭沒收120萬元定金離場，成為項目首宗撻定個案。<br />\n<br />\n一手成交紀錄冊顯示，瓏珀山Queen Tower 2 16樓A室，實用面積1,103方呎，四房間隔，在本月22日以2,400萬元招標售出，呎價21,758元。付款細項中列明，買家可獲9%稅務回贈，料成交時扣除回贈實際樓價為2,184萬元，呎價19,800元。不過，交易最新顯示簽臨約後無進展，該買家料損失樓價5%定金，即120萬元離場，成為項目首宗撻定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，瓏珀山今日沽出7個單位，單位實用面積介乎974至1,502方呎，成交價1,968.116萬元至3,126萬元，呎價18,288元至26,446元。最貴一伙是Queen Tower 1 6樓Garden Suite B，屬四房間隔，實用面積1,182方呎，連586方呎花園，成交價3,216萬元，呎價26,447元，呎價創項目新高。單位買家同樣享9%回贈，料實際成交價為2,844.66萬元，呎價24,066元。"},{"pid":"8deb3f1e84fb4fa6f6d47d6b19f0fd6686384bac","tid":2510782,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"新盤撻訂資訊少疑問多 重推成交才更新？難知撻訂金額？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bfba8e093f1a75ffef81b71071732128ba4b8c31","tid":2510782,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8deb3f1e84fb4fa6f6d47d6b19f0fd6686384bac","tid":2510782,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"新盤撻訂資訊少疑問多 重推成交才更新？難知撻訂金額？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}